<div class="title">Middle Aged Guy Has Perfect Morning</div>
<div class="substance">2C-T-2</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Antiquus&Exact=1">Antiquus</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Antiquus. "Middle Aged Guy Has Perfect Morning: An Experience with 2C-T-2 (exp4061)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 9, 2000. erowid.org/exp/4061</div>

